---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Cognitogram Labs">
  <main class="about">
    <header>
      <p class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">~</a>/about</p>
      <h1>Cognitogram Labs</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="content">
      <blockquote class="quote">
        <p>“The real test of a theory is its ability to predict.”</p>
        <cite>— Richard Feynman</cite>
      </blockquote>
      <p>
        This principle anchors our approach to whole brain emulation. We build AI models that predict
        future neural activity, training large-scale architectures on extensive, perturbed data
        captured at single-neuron resolution.
      </p>
      <p>
        We transform these models into instruments for uncovering the brain's dynamics. Embracing the
        bitter lesson (that scale and learning outperform hand-crafted solutions) charts our path
        toward human brain emulation and, ultimately, mind uploading.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="contact">
      <p class="label">Contact</p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@cognitogram.com">hello@cognitogram.com</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
    padding: 6rem 3rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  header {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .content {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .content p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .quote {
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .quote p {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .quote cite {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .contact a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .contact a:hover {
    border-color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
